long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you tired of having 100+ tabs cluttering your browser by the end of the day? We understand that some tabs are valuable while others are just distractions. That's where Tab Brain comes in – it effortlessly gathers all your tabs and neatly organizes them by domain, simplifying the process of decluttering. Say goodbye to those unnecessary tabs like "thank you for joining this zoom meeting" with just a single click.

Clear the clutter and focus on what truly matters in your day. Get Tab Brain now!

Update: Moved the notifications for deleted tabs to the middle of the screen so they don't block the sidebar
